3Q","Bekijk Cloud Communications - secondary - https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/grootzakelijk/smart-combinations/cloud-communications.htm","Bekijk Cloud Communications",{"id":553,"objectType":21,"contentType":144,"name":554,"url":554},"5q5S6O34jGgVZDeE6fM8da","https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/grootzakelijk/smart-combinations/cloud-communications.htm",{"title":149,"subtitle":178,"richText":179},{"title":68,"subtitle":149},{"id":558,"objectType":21,"contentType":76,"name":559,"theme":32,"layout":560,"column1":561,"column2":652,"flow":150,"spacingOverride":69,"autoScale":33,"cardifyColumn1":381,"cardifyColumn2":381,"notificationPosition":70,"includeInAnchorMenu":17,"heading":677,"reverseFirstColumnOnMobile":17},"52bgfdzRTn1GxPkyEDMk8k","Subtle grey - 67/33 - Cloud - FAQ","67% - 33%",[562],{"id":563,"objectType":21,"contentType":564,"name":565,"title":566,"list1":567,"heading":651},"1SVPcKupHrGYAokWrdZTk8","faqBlock","Veelgestelde vragen over cloud","Veelgestelde vragen cloud",[568,597,630],{"id":569,"objectType":21,"contentType":570,"name":571,"title":572,"text":573,"imagePosition":596},"50TEgdgs4upvsGSSGkVLB3","faqItem","Wat is een cloud server? - Cloud","Wat is een cloud server?",{"data":574,"content":575,"nodeType":133},{},[576],{"data":577,"content":578,"nodeType":118},{},[579,583,593],{"data":580,"marks":581,"value":582,"nodeType":117},{},[],"Een cloud server is een computer ‘ergens op internet’ die bedrijven gebruiken om hun applicaties op te draaien, gegevens op te verwerken en bestanden op te slaan. Meer weten? ",{"data":584,"content":592,"nodeType":478},{"target":585},{"id":586,"objectType":21,"contentType":137,"name":587,"text":588,"type":280,"linkPresentation":141,"link":589,"anchorSection":147},"76ia2T0WdPTc82kaBRA255","Lees meer over cloud servers - textlink - https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/blog/cloud-server-versus-eigen-server-dit-zijn-de-verschillen.htm","Lees meer over cloud servers",{"id":590,"objectType":21,"contentType":144,"name":591,"url":591,"target":146},"tcY2p2xOxUZrOSMw3pA7u","https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/blog/cloud-server-versus-eigen-server-dit-zijn-de-verschillen.htm",[],{"data":594,"marks":595,"value":51,"nodeType":117},{},[],"right",{"id":598,"objectType":21,"contentType":570,"name":599,"title":600,"text":601,"imagePosition":596},"2P3SjSPwscNhT77EetwDEg","Een managed cloud. Wat is dat? - Cloud","Een managed cloud. Wat is dat?",{"data":602,"content":603,"nodeType":133},{},[604,611],{"data":605,"content":606,"nodeType":118},{},[607],{"data":608,"marks":609,"value":610,"nodeType":117},{},[],"De managed cloud stelt organisaties in staat om het werk dat in de private en public cloud wordt gedaan centraal te beheren. Welke hybride cloudstrategie ook wordt ingezet, data moeten altijd beschikbaar zijn. Wanneer applicaties en workloads over verschillende infrastructuren worden verplaatst, is een veilige back-up essentieel. Een storing of uitval van systemen mag de business niet in gevaar brengen. Managed hybrid cloud moet balans brengen tussen flexibiliteit, veiligheid en kostenefficiency. ",{"data":612,"content":613,"nodeType":118},{},[614,618,627],{"data":615,"marks":616,"value":617,"nodeType":117},{},[],"Meer weten? ",{"data":619,"content":626,"nodeType":478},{"target":620},{"id":621,"objectType":21,"contentType":137,"name":622,"text":623,"type":280,"linkPresentation":141,"link":624,"anchorSection":147},"4138fZE7Jq3V02Z6mf0TZY","Lees meer over de managed cloud. - textlink - https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/microsoft-365.htm","Lees meer over de managed cloud. ",{"id":625,"objectType":21,"contentType":144,"name":437,"url":437,"target":146},"148LIyOEnlNuuDdWwV6iev",[],{"data":628,"marks":629,"value":51,"nodeType":117},{},[],{"id":631,"objectType":21,"contentType":570,"name":632,"title":633,"text":634,"imagePosition":596},"1pQTbVKZBoSydjRIh4HpGK","Voorbeelden van cloud toepassingen - Cloud","Voorbeelden van cloud toepassingen",{"data":635,"content":636,"nodeType":133},{},[637,644],{"data":638,"content":639,"nodeType":118},{},[640],{"data":641,"marks":642,"value":643,"nodeType":117},{},[],"Het bekendste zijn SaaS, IaaS en PaaS. Bij Software as a Service (SaaS) huurt men van een leverancier software die via internet wordt gedistribueerd. Dit gebeurt meestal door middel van een abonnement. De cloud provider zorgt dat de software tijdig upgrades en beveiligingspatches krijgt.",{"data":645,"content":646,"nodeType":118},{},[647],{"data":648,"marks":649,"value":650,"nodeType":117},{},[],"Al dit vervelende werk wordt de gebruiker uit handen genomen. Ook hoeft hij zich niet druk te maken over de onderliggende infrastructuur. De provider regelt dit allemaal. Salesforce werkt bijvoorbeeld volgens dit model.",{"title":68,"item":149,"richText":178},[653],{"id":654,"objectType":21,"contentType":104,"name":655,"isVerticalView":33,"title":656,"description":657,"navigation":667,"heading":676},"4em6Pt6z1wi4sagTYzjAnD","Andere vragen? - Cloud - primary","Andere vraag?",{"data":658,"content":659,"nodeType":133},{},[660],{"data":661,"content":662,"nodeType":118},{},[663],{"data":664,"marks":665,"value":666,"nodeType":117},{},[],"Op onze servicepagina vind je alles wat je zoekt over het installeren- en gebruik van clouddiensten. ",[668],{"id":669,"objectType":21,"contentType":137,"name":670,"text":671,"type":140,"buttonPresentation":672,"linkPresentation":141,"link":673,"anchorSection":147},"3LwIbdhNpjgaimZHiNAUe9","Naar service - primary - https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/service/cloud.htm","Naar service","primary",{"id":674,"objectType":21,"contentType":144,"name":675,"url":675,"target":146},"6PzTtYwAVrZTcSIBXxnHXm","https://www.kpn.com/zakelijk/service/cloud.htm",{"title":68,"richText":149},{"title":68,"subtitle":68},"Clouddiensten | Veilig werken in de Cloud ","Werk overal veilig en zorgeloos samen met clouddiensten als Office 365, Exchange Online of Back-Up Online met de clouddiensten van KPN.","/zakelijk/cloud.htm",["Set"],["ShallowReactive",683],{},{}]</script>
